# Environment Variables Configuration for Google Docs Clone

## Clerk Authentication
# Get these from https://dashboard.clerk.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your_clerk_publishable_key
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=your_clerk_secret_key
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/login
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/signup
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL=/notes
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL=/notes

## Convex Backend
# Get these from https://convex.dev
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=your_convex_deployment_url

## Liveblocks - Real-time Collaboration
# Get these from https://liveblocks.io
NEXT_PUBLIC_LIVEBLOCKS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_liveblocks_public_key

## Y.js WebSocket Provider for Collaborative Editing
# For local development, you can use ws://localhost:1234
# For production, use a hosted Y WebSocket provider
NEXT_PUBLIC_YWEBSOCKET_ENDPOINT=ws://localhost:1234
